DJI Tello Drone Control with Python

This project demonstrates how to control a DJI Tello drone using Python. It includes basic flight commands, live video streaming, and automated flight patterns. Ideal for beginners exploring drone programming and automation.



- Connect to the Tello drone via Wi-Fi
- Send flight commands using Python
- Stream live video from the droneâ€™s camera
- Automate flight routines for demos or testing


